12
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,950
After the ceremony,

13
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,280
you'll top the harem

14
00:01:34,950 --> 00:01:36,000
as you wish.

15
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,150
And your son, the Seventh Prince,

16
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,680
will become the Crown Prince.

17
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,840
The future of the Zhao Family

18
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,400
lies on you, Master Tao.

19
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:56,990
But

20
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:58,760
