If the Empress's son ascends the throne,

60
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,750
what will happen

61
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:40,520
to your son,

62
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:42,910
his former biggest rival?

63
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:46,240
What about the long-lasting

64
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,430
and prominent Zhao Family?

65
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:56,060
(Xingshan Hall)

66
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,430
What will happen to Min?

67
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:03,710
She'll lead a miserable life.

68
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,080
She can't get anything she wants,

69
00:04:06,650 --> 00:04:07,870
