86
00:04:57,820 --> 00:04:59,610
If so, I'll do it.

87
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:01,900
I'll be the Saintess, Mother.

88
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,640
Min,

89
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:07,430
I'll forever adore you and love you.

90
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,870
I'll give you anything you want.

91
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:15,360
You'll be the most-loved princess.

92
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:19,860
You're the best, Mother.

93
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,470
Your Highness,

94
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:33,670
the Princess went in

95
