121
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,360
If you like it,

122
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:14,120
- I'll have it sent to your place.
- No problem.

123
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,750
Thank you.

124
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:20,700
(Xingshan Hall)

125
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:45,840
Min!

126
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:49,630
Go back with me.

127
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,680
I won't.

128
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,670
It's overdue for 15 years.

129
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,600
It has to be done today.

130
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,200
What are you saying?

131
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,800
Let's go.

132
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,670
What am I saying?

133
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,960
Don't you know the best, Mother?

134
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,440
Lu Jiu,

135
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:11,030
Princess Duanyang is possessed.

136
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:12,390
Take her away now.

137
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,390
Lu Jiu!

138
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,000
Are you defying me?

139
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,510
Let's go!

140
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,630
Ruoshi...!

141
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:29,190
Min...!

142
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,360
It's time.

143
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,080
Tao Ying?

144
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,160
It's you!

145
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:41,720
You're manipulating her
with your witchcraft, aren't you?

146
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,240
You won't succeed!

147
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:10,360
(Incubus Demon)
Tao Ying died ten years ago.

148
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,960
Your Highness,

149
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:14,670
did Mu Huaijiang not tell you

150
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,840
that Tao Ying was a mere puppet?

151
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:18,110
I am

152
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:21,120
the mastermind behind everything.

153
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,840
Demon! Demon!

154
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,080
Guards!

155
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:27,910
Catch that demon!

156
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,960
Help! Catch that demon!

157
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,790
Finally, this day has come.

158
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,910
Everyone in this hall

159
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:36,960
will die a worthy death today.

160
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,320
Chief,

161
00:11:00,330 --> 00:11:01,410
the Life Suction Formation

162
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,550
is about to be activated.

163
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:05,120
Stand by. Get ready to assist.

164
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:08,200
Stick to Cultivator Mu's plan.

165
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,960
Dowager Consort Zhao is there, too.

166
00:11:10,150 --> 00:11:11,550
If something happens to her,

167
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,600
His Majesty will punish us...

168
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:15,910
Cultivator Mu has told me

169
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:17,550
about the situation
with a Message Charm.

170
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,840
Relax. It's fine.

171
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:19,990
Chief,

172
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:21,080
the stakes are high.

173
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:23,120
Do you really believe
in those civilians?

174
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,750
Absolutely.

175
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,680
You evil demon.

176
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:35,240
Do you think your plan is working?

177
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,840
Look around.

178
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:38,110
Are those guests

179
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:39,550
in panic?

180
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,440
You look vigorous, General Li.

181
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,440
Chancellor,

182
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:48,840
please look after my son
at the Imperial College.

183
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,480
Sure, sure.

184
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:53,360
- Look at this fabric.
- Mr. Liu,

185
00:11:53,370 --> 00:11:55,150
- It's of top quality.
- I'll have to rely on you.

186
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,840
I have some more at home.

187
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,750
- If you like it,
- Sure, sure.

188
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,270
I'll have it sent to your place.

189
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,320
Thank you.

190
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,680
Look,

191
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,560
your plan failed.

192
00:12:32,910 --> 00:12:34,550
To gain immortality

193
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:35,550
with this formation,

194
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:38,000
you'll need hundreds of lives.

195
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:40,360
But now other than us

196
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:41,870
and Dowager Consort Zhao,

197
00:12:42,510 --> 00:12:44,390
only the bride and the groom are here.

198
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:45,790
Who are you?

199
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:51,630
I always tell the demons

200
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,630
who are going to kill them.

201
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,160
I'm a Mu from Huainan,

202
00:12:55,870 --> 00:12:56,710
Mu Yao.

203
00:12:58,030 --> 00:12:59,000
One of the Mu Family?

204
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:01,630
15 years ago,

205
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:03,670
Mu Huaijiang ruined my plan!

206
00:13:03,670 --> 00:13:04,910
Now, you!

207
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:06,840
At first, I thought

208
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,270
it was the powerful Resentful Woman.

209
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:09,910
Turns out,

210
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:12,510
you're only a Tier 4 Incubus Demon.

211
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,690
Making such an elaborate plan

212
00:13:13,870 --> 00:13:15,550
to catch you is a complete waste.

213
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,550
But that's fine.

214
00:13:18,390 --> 00:13:19,720
It's worth it for the safety

215
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,000
of the people.

216
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,240
The formation has been activated.

217
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:25,000
Your demon core will solidify

218
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,320
and appear at the core of the formation.

219
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,390
It'll be so fragile

220
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,510
that a little child

221
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,080
can easily break it.

222
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,040
Here it comes.

223
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:49,480
The dark energy is...

224
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:50,680
Resentment.

225
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,040
15 years ago,

226
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,840
over 400 people were killed here.

227
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:58,270
Lingering resentment, obsession, hatred

228
00:13:58,870 --> 00:14:00,440
and other painful

229
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,510
and twisted feelings

230
00:14:01,900 --> 00:14:02,870
can be forged in the demon core

231
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:04,030
to boost demonic power.

232
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:05,360
That explains it.

233
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,440
With such energy,

234
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:09,510
his demon core is unbreakable.

235
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:12,480
It's a pity that the pain
of those people's tragic deaths

236
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:15,000
is now fueling his evildoing.

237
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,670
Demon Catchers,

238
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:19,000
you've underestimated me.

239
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:22,120
Even if I can't reach immortality today,

240
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,750
you can't do anything to me,

241
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,240
but you'll

242
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:29,000
all die here!

243
00:14:53,630 --> 00:14:54,550
How beautiful.

244
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:04,710
Your Highness,

245
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,040
where are we?

246
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,030
I... I don't know.

247
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,390
Why are you asking me?

248
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:11,600
Of course you know.

249
00:15:12,370 --> 00:15:13,230
We're

250
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,240
in your dream.

251
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:15,510
Nonsense!

252
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:16,750
A Tier 7 Incubus Demon

253
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:18,150
can create a nightmare

254
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,280
and trap people inside forever.

255
00:15:19,670 --> 00:15:21,000
This one is merely Tier 4.

256
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:21,920
Normally, he can't do that.

257
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,400
But with the strong resentment

258
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:24,480
in his demon core,

259
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,480
he's as powerful as a Tier 7 Incubus Demon.

260
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:27,840
Resentment

261
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,550
flows to its source.

262
00:15:30,270 --> 00:15:31,110
Dowager Consort Zhao,

263
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,720
we are in your nightmare.

264
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,440
Mother,

265
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:36,630
this place is so beautiful and peaceful.

266
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:38,600
Why is it your nightmare?

267
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:40,750
Where exactly are we?

268
00:15:44,790 --> 00:15:45,630
I don't know.

269
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,030
Stop asking me!

270
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,000
I know nothing about it.

271
00:15:50,910 --> 00:15:51,910
A perfect habitat for demons

272
00:15:52,150 --> 00:15:53,150
in such a remote place.

273
00:15:53,790 --> 00:15:54,630
This is

274
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:55,840
the Qilin Mountain.

275
00:15:56,600 --> 00:15:57,510
The Qilin Mountain?

276
00:15:59,120 --> 00:15:59,960
Are we in

277
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:01,320
the Qilin Mountain?

278
00:16:24,510 --> 00:16:25,350
Mother,

279
00:16:26,030 --> 00:16:27,910
isn't that you from years ago?

280
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:43,150
Level this evil mountain

281
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:46,840
with ten mountain talismans.

282
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:50,000
Let no demons go.

283
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:51,590
Yes.

284
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:40,030
Ten mountain talismans?

285
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:41,070
Why?

286
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:44,550
It's a demon lair.

287
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,790
Do I need a reason to kill demons?

288
00:17:47,270 --> 00:17:49,270
They were produced by natural energy.

289
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,030
They never left here or did evil.

290
00:17:52,350 --> 00:17:53,310
Demons are like beasts.

291
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:55,510
I'm a consort.

292
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:57,440
