322
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:23,480
or why I don't remember

323
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,590
about my trip,

324
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:28,270
or what happened to me.

325
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:31,210
But now

326
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,470
I'm dying.

327
00:19:33,830 --> 00:19:35,440
I have one last wish.

328
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,640
Tell me,

329
00:19:39,590 --> 00:19:41,310
was I in love with someone,

330
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:44,430
