332
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:51,160
Why are you asking that

333
00:19:52,830 --> 00:19:54,200
at this point?

334
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:56,800
Sister...

335
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:00,400
please

336
00:20:02,110 --> 00:20:03,030
tell me.

337
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:05,720
Why do I always feel

338
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:09,110
