339
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:13,480
Did I lose someone I loved?

340
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:15,760
Sister...

341
00:20:18,110 --> 00:20:19,720
You're the Seventh Prince's uncle

342
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:22,000
and the Master of the Zhao Family.

343
00:20:22,590 --> 00:20:24,590
You're at the top of the pyramid.

344
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:27,160
You aren't involved with any demon

345
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,880
whatsoever.

346
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:47,560
Qinghuan!

347
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:49,280
Qinghuan!

348
00:20:50,070 --> 00:20:51,000
Qinghuan!

349
00:20:54,550 --> 00:20:55,440
Qinghuan!

