00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:57,830
Qinghuan!

351
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,510
Qinghuan!

352
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:06,640
Qinghuan!

353
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:10,270
Qinghuan!

354
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,270
So

355
00:21:21,640 --> 00:21:25,350
the late Marquis was away
for a long time

356
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:26,880
before getting married

357
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:28,790
