365
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:49,400
I did all that for you.

366
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:50,720
Min,

367
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:51,720
Ruoshi,

368
00:21:52,240 --> 00:21:54,480
I had to protect the Zhao Family.

369
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:57,810
As the new Master,

370
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,730
Qinghuan was bewitched

371
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:01,030
