384
00:22:26,350 --> 00:22:27,190
The Worry-Free Curse

385
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:29,270
can erase one's memory,

386
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:30,920
but not one's love or hatred.

387
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,720
The late Marquis died with regrets

388
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,280
because of you.

389
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,000
It became your nightmare

390
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,110
