407
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:09,270
Were your brother being with a demon,

408
00:23:09,390 --> 00:23:11,460
could you still remain untroubled

409
00:23:12,450 --> 00:23:13,590
and lenient?

410
00:23:13,590 --> 00:23:14,960
Could you do that?

411
00:23:21,060 --> 00:23:22,740
