412
00:23:30,020 --> 00:23:31,200
The Xingshan Hall?

413
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,960
It's the one in her dream.

414
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:35,280
Finally,

415
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,830
