424
00:24:18,030 --> 00:24:18,870
Very well.

425
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:22,920
Her figure and looks match Min's, too.

426
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,350
The Blessing Ceremony is tomorrow.

427
00:24:26,110 --> 00:24:27,240
Use her to see how it goes.

428
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:30,270
We've been warned of the importance.

429
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,240
We shall tread carefully.

430
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,400
The Saintess

431
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:48,640
should be pious for the prayer
to be answered.

432
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:51,400
Do you want to be the Saintess?

433
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:53,430
Yes.

434
00:24:53,790 --> 00:24:55,640
I really do.

435
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,240
I want to be the Saintess,

436
00:24:57,510 --> 00:24:59,720
so Your Highness will give us money

437
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:01,240
to pay for my sister's treatment.

438
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:04,480
Thank you, Your Highness.

439
00:26:10,590 --> 00:26:11,590
