440
00:26:12,510 --> 00:26:13,480
I once saw

441
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,720
that rattle-drum.

442
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,000
Peiyun

443
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:17,400
carried it with her all the time.

444
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:21,110
