Peiyu.

445
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:24,310
So this girl is her sister, Peiyu!

446
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:26,720
Peiyun?

447
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:29,750
She...

448
00:26:31,550 --> 00:26:32,390
Did she

449
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,030
come to the palace

450
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,270
