453
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,480
You're vicious,

454
00:26:49,110 --> 00:26:50,030
but not too dumb.

455
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:52,000
I remember it.

456
00:26:53,070 --> 00:26:55,200
