459
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:00,720
No!

460
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,510
I love you the most!

461
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,750
You know that, Min.

462
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,880
I'd never sacrifice you.

463
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,720
So you sacrificed another girl?

464
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,030
She was from a poor family.

465
00:27:09,550 --> 00:27:10,550
I paid her family

466
00:27:11,030 --> 00:27:12,830
