467
00:27:13,830 --> 00:27:14,790
In your eyes,

468
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:16,400
demons are mere nothing.

469
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:18,150
So are humans,

470
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:19,520
I guess.

471
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:20,960
- I...
- You used another girl

472
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:23,270
instead of your daughter
to be the Saintess.

473
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:25,240
Did you already know

474
00:27:25,510 --> 00:27:26,550
there'd be a fire

475
00:27:27,030 --> 00:27:28,200
