476
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:29,550
at the Blessing Ceremony?

477
00:27:30,590 --> 00:27:31,680
I built this hall

478
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,790
to pray for the people's welfare

479
00:27:34,110 --> 00:27:35,640
and well-being!

480
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:37,750
That wizard Tao Ying

481
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:40,310
colluded with that demon

482
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:41,880
and fooled me.

483
00:27:42,590 --> 00:27:44,880
I knew nothing about their plot, really!

484
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:45,840
At this point,

485
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:47,110
