486
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,310
as if you've done evil

487
00:27:48,580 --> 00:27:49,420
for the right cause

488
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,280
and it's others' fault.

489
00:27:50,350 --> 00:27:51,350
It is their fault!

490
00:27:51,550 --> 00:27:53,270
I didn't know anything. I swear!

491
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:54,350
I didn't do it.

492
00:27:54,350 --> 00:27:55,590
I didn't know.

493
00:27:55,590 --> 00:27:56,680
Stop asking me!

494
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,110
They lied to me.

495
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,010
I didn't know...

496
00:27:59,510 --> 00:28:01,520
I swear I knew nothing at all!

497
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,320
Mother,

498
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:17,110
