505
00:28:28,770 --> 00:28:29,650
Why?

506
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:35,590
That was an accident.

507
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:38,030
The court concluded the case.

508
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:40,030
An unfortunate accident.

509
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:42,200
You keep lying to us.

510
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:43,760
20 years ago,

511
00:28:44,310 --> 00:28:46,000
to break up your brother and his love,

512
00:28:46,830 --> 00:28:49,000
you had the Astronomical Bureau
level the Qilin Mountain.

513
00:28:50,270 --> 00:28:51,790
I've checked Tao Ying out.

514
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:53,430
He and his daughter

515
00:28:53,830 --> 00:28:55,070
had been living in seclusion there

516
00:28:56,110 --> 00:28:57,720
until you gave that order,

517
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,000
causing his daughter

518
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:00,590
to be killed in that catastrophe.

519
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:02,790
That blood-stained wooden doll

520
00:29:03,510 --> 00:29:04,400
was left

521
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:05,790
by her.

522
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:08,790
Tao Ying wasn't a demon.

523
00:29:09,550 --> 00:29:11,160
He and the Incubus Demon who used him

524
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:13,270
came to you for revenge.

525
00:29:14,110 --> 00:29:15,160
You did evil

526
00:29:15,550 --> 00:29:16,390
for your selfish desires.

527
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:17,720
To cover that up,

528
00:29:18,070 --> 00:29:19,310
you did it again,

529
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:21,510
leading you to a vicious circle,

530
00:29:21,790 --> 00:29:22,880
the depths of vice,

531
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:25,110
and eventually, the massacre by fire.

532
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:26,430
Zhao Qinru,

533
00:29:26,750 --> 00:29:29,030
do you think you can atone for your sins

534
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:31,000
simply by playing a philanthropist?

535
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,160
If you don't tell the truth,

536
00:29:33,110 --> 00:29:34,750
we'll forever be trapped in the nightmare.

537
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,720
Resentment is a personal feeling.

538
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:38,030
