575
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:37,440
It can't hurt people in reality,

576
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:39,520
but we're in the dream.

577
00:31:40,110 --> 00:31:40,950
Dreams come from

578
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,160
one's mind.

579
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,040
So

580
00:31:44,270 --> 00:31:45,110
the resentment here

581
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:47,920
